00:55:08,317 --> 00:55:09,996
Ibu Dong-hyun.

744
00:55:10,413 --> 00:55:13,767
Ya, dia masuk.

745
00:55:13,792 --> 00:55:15,809
Dia masuk Universitas Katolik.

746
00:55:15,834 --> 00:55:17,922
Semua berkat Buddha.

747
00:55:17,947 --> 00:55:19,489
Avalokitesvara.

748
00:55:22,960 --> 00:55:24,244
Cepat kemari.

749
00:55:24,268 --> 00:55:29,071
